Kriti Sanon is an Indian actress and model who primarily works in the Hindi film industry, also known as Bollywood. Kriti made her acting debut in Bollywood with the film "Heropanti" in 2014, for which she received critical acclaim and a Filmfare Award for Best Female Debut. Since her debut, Kriti has appeared in a variety of successful films. Some of her notable movies include "Dilwale," "Bareilly Ki Barfi," "Luka Chuppi," "Housefull 4," and "Panipat." Along with her acting career, Kriti has also worked as a model and has appeared in various commercial campaigns and magazine covers.
